content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #81626 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

This issue was fixed in nightly only, so now is a beta regression, tomorrow will be discussed in the meeting.

Assuming the P-medium for #81658 still stands, I think the same can be applied also for this one.
Could we consider backporting the PR that fixed it (#82297)? (I don't have much context, so maybe that isn't possible for some reason.)
Me neither, but I /think/ Felix is planning to ask the compiler team to cast a vote at the meeting obout reverting #81473 and patching the diagnostics on nightly
